<div class="container">
    <div class="section row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h3 class="headline headline--beta">Ready to speak at WordCamp Europe?</h3>
            <p>
                Are you ready to speak on the biggest WordPress stage in Europe?
            </p>
            <p>WordCamp Europe is the largest WordPress event in Europe bringing all local communities together. We are
                looking for speakers on a wide variety of topics and backgrounds. Are you ready to take to the stage in
                Belgrade? Do you have a story to tell? Do you have expertise in a specific field to share? We want to
                hear from you!
            </p>
            <p>
                We are looking for long talks, lightning talks, and workshops that bring value to our WordPress
                audience. We want <strong>talks and workshops</strong> to appeal to developers, designers, bloggers, business owners,
                site builders, translators, community organisers, and everything in between. Looking for talk ideas?
                Check out our <a href="{{ url('talk_ideas') }}">list of topics</a>. Need more ideas for workshops, check
                out <a href="{{ url('workshops') }}">this list</a>.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h3 class="headline headline--beta">Format and Application Process</h3>
            <p><strong>You can apply for the following format:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Long talks – 40 minutes total (30 mins for talk & 10 mins for questions).</li>
                <li>Lightning talks – 10 mins for talk & 5 mins for questions</li>
                <li>Workshops – 90 minutes or 3 hours long.</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>These are the key dates you need to know:</strong></p>
            <ol>
                <li>Call for speakers and workshops will be open until 15 January</li>
                <li>We will then be selecting speakers and workshops until late February</li>
                <li>Selected speakers and workshop hosts will be informed starting 1 March</li>
                <li>Speaker and workshop announcements will start mid to late March</li>
            </ol>
            <p>
                <a href="{{ url('speaker_package') }}">Read more about the speaker selection process.</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

